This script will unbind and bind the Network virtualized device
for as many times as specified by the user

Inputs Needed (in multiplexer file):
------------------------------------
device_ip - The IP used to configure the Network virtualized device for ping test
netmask - The netmask value
peer_ip - IP of the peer to verify network connectivity after unbind/bind
count - The number of times the unbind and bind test has to be executed

NOTE: The last device listed by "ip link show" will be used to configure and test the
driver unbind/bind functionality
